                "content": "My English reference book mainly consists of roots, small grammar points, good sentences, sentence patterns, phrases, etc., learned in class.\n                    I write down things that are easily forgotten so they can be useful when writing compositions.",
                "image": "https://github.com/kelvinlinkk/portfolio/raw/main/英文學習歷程/note/英文筆記.jpg",
